            </connector>
            <label>Planned Start Date Time is blank</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <description>Update fields on Volunteer Hours - End Date, Planned Start Date Time and Contact &gt; Volunteer Status. Migrated from,
1. Volunteer Hours - Set End Date WF.
2. Volunteer Hours - Set Planned Start Date &amp; Time WF
3. ascend Set Active Volunteer Status PB</description>
